Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是再多躺一下子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说我回来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好渴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绕去哪家店坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,要不要一起去暍茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还得整理记录
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等小瞳一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别去当电灯泡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,那样不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要当电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼的由加莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\N拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见了,由加莉\N先走啰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到月亮与地球\N同时在天上出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个浪漫主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会作那样的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的坠子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我祖母的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像这样子摆动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就会像钟摆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一秒一次地,一直摆动下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晓得…接下来会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长会摆动起坠子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 3 4 56
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:04:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 8 9 10
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 1 12 13 14…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,我在叫你耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说句话嘛,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕月堂的草莓麻缮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铄仓屋的起司蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南本铺的铜锣烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义大利传统店的薄荷冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上每天奉上不同的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放过你这次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那天…那个命运之日的前一天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜她曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湘南小馆的肉丁洋葱烩饭超级好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸色很不好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经知道了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有算过你跟学长的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是算出来的结果不好的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉,你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜欢的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要是喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是早点表白吧\N由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不小心听到学长他们的聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说天野学长可能会去国外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他父亲的工作所以得到英国去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能连县大会都没办法参加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是早点表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不说一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你那么喜欢天野学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人模不着头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是被寨巴哈抓走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是靠多伦卡喀的科学力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能制造出光柱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小瞳是到哪去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很想回幻之月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样对我们来说不是正好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来,寨巴哈也无法敔动命运改变装置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈…寨巴哈军在国境布下了重兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测不到少女的反应,多伦卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我的梦想就是无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,洗澡水放好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你一直…一直都喜欢学长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为自己对学长是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来打算要守护她…守护小瞳一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她却离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的心境为何会如此平静?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的离去确实让我感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我同样为她能回到,自己的世界感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为她很像妹妹很像谢蕾娜的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这张牌会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要回去那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想再回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,您是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很在意小瞳的事,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在意她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您编人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都待在您身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以对您再清楚不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很在意小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喜欢小瞳,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人,看来您还没察觉到\N自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家从好久以前就晓得了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳不也总是那么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"意念一定能传达得到"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以您的意念一定会传达得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能传达给小瞳知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是谢蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然十年不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我绝不会错认自己的妹妹,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得她至今都流落何方,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还失去了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了记忆?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我外出征战的这段时间家妹就劳烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是天空骑士的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我在皇宫照顾她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧,谢蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是幻人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾久卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别走,迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪兰度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾,我并不清楚他的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能确定的是,他的背后似乎有魔导士在操控
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔导士?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接听命于多伦卡喀的寨巴哈的科学家们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾听说他们为了改变\N人的命运而进行人体实验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把捉来的小孩子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体实验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢蕾娜竟然是被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已经知道牛顿是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到苹果从树上掉落\N才发现万有引力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其实牛顿还对炼金术及魔法多有涉猎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呼唤着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多伦卡喀大人,已经准备就绪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让龙与少女的引力升华
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就能够产生命运素粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,引力仍存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女一定会再度现身于盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话,天野学长就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我没能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是最好的朋友却没能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想见他,我想再见他一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运素粒子达临界点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置敔动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我要再见你一次面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎,你准备好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇气…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7  8…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,我不会再让你离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个纷争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:23:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对幸运圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.54,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:05.99,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:13.62,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:19.77,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:22.13,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:27.14,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.98,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:34.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:38.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:42.29,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:49.76,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:05.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:13.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:19.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:22.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:34.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:38.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:42.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:49.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


